    <p class="Subheading">Using Ji Bytes on different devices</p>
        
    <p class="normal">For an optimal learning experience, we recommend that Ji Bytes be used on a desktop or laptop. If you are using a mobile device, you will not get the full intended Ji Bytes experience.</p>
    <li class="normal"><strong> Browser</strong>: Ji Bytes should be used in Safari, Chrome or Firefox on a Mac or PC</li>
        <li class="normal"><strong>Mobile</strong>: A limited Ji Bytes can be used on your iPad or iPhone’s Safari browser. Android devices are <strong>not</strong> supported.
    </li>
    </p>
