    <ul>
    
        <li class="normal">Go to <a href="https://jitap.net/activities/" target="_blank">Ji Tap</a>&nbsp;</li>
        <li class="normal">Make sure that you have a parent login to Ji Tap - signup is free (<a href="https://youtu.be/89mRwNQcWEk" target="_blank">Watch how to create a family profile</a>)&nbsp;</li>
