        <p class="subsubheading">Ji Studio</p>
        <p class="normal">You can use Ji Studio to create interactive books and posters which can be printed as PDFs or shared.</p>
        <ul><li class="normal">Desktop/laptop: You will need to <a href="http://info.jewishinteractive.org/ji-studio-2" target="_blank">download the Ji Studio app</a> to your computer and install it. This will take a few minutes, depending on your internet connection. Once installed, it can be used offline.</li>
            <li class="normal">iPad/iPhone: Download the <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ji-studio-4-jewish-kids/id839491165" target="_blank">Ji Studio 4 Jewish Kids</a> app. Once installed, it can be used offline.</li>
            <li class="normal"><a href="https://youtu.be/lrDUW6gqoGs" target="_blank">Watch video</a> about Ji Studio.</li>
        </ul>
        
    <p class="subsubheading">Adobe Spark!</p>
